markets.title: Will a NEPA permitting reform bill become law by January 02, 2023?
markets.rules_primary: If a NEPA (National Environmental Policy Act) permitting reform bill becomes law by January 02, 2023 according to Congress.gov, then the market resolves to Yes.
markets.rules_secondary:
The market will expire at the sooner of the first 10 AM ET following the occurrence of the event, the first 10 AM ET following the release of data for January 02, 2023 or one week after January 02, 2023.

PLEASE SEE THE RULEBOOK FOR THE COMPLETE DEFINITION OF A NEPA PERMITTING REFORM BILL.
